cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper focuses on dialogue systems and natural language processing, which are core topics in this sub-category.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Deep learning techniques are widely used in dialogue systems, and this sub-category covers research on AI and machine learning.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Deep learning is a subfield of machine learning, and this sub-category covers research on various machine learning techniques.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): Dialogue systems are software systems, and this sub-category covers research on software development and engineering.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): Dialogue systems are designed to interact with humans, and this sub-category covers research on the interaction between humans and computers.
